  "title": "Customer Service Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Salary:</strong> $2,500</p><p><strong>Job Description:</strong><br />We are seeking a results-driven Customer Service Executive to join our team. This role involves engaging with clients, explaining service offerings, and managing inquiries professionally. Candidates should be detail-oriented and able to maintain strong client relationships.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Engage with potential customers and and explain the firm's services</li><li>Handle inquiries, quotations, and sales negotiations professionally.</li><li>Maintain accurate sales records using Microsoft Excel, PowerPoint, and Word.</li><li>Build and maintain strong relationships with clients.</li><li>Collaborate with internal teams to ensure seamless customer service.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office Suite (Excel, PowerPoint, Word).</li><li>Strong communication skills </li><li>Goal-oriented with a customer-focused attitude.</li></ul><p><strong>Benefits:</strong></p><ul><li>14 days AL</li><li>Medical Claims & Benefits</li><li>Annual Company Overseas Trip</li></ul><p>Teo Jian Rong<br />EA No. 25S2769<br />EA Personnel No. R1768774</p>",
